snippet.title: Fatal Fury City of Wolves - Release Date Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Watch the release date trailer for SNK's upcoming fighting game, Fatal Fury City of Wolves, coming to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X/S, Steam, and the Epic Games Store on April 24, 2025.
